intelligence, G, because that&#39;s what the Raven’s Progressive Matrices and other tests are designed

2
00:00:15,980 --> 00:00:17,220
to measure.

3
00:00:17,220 --> 00:00:21,510
There is actually a way where we can basically tell whether intelligence is one thing or

4
00:00:21,510 --> 00:00:23,020
multiple things.

5
00:00:23,020 --> 00:00:27,690
And it is to do with comparing people’s performance on many different tests of intelligence,

6
00:00:27,690 --> 00:00:32,570
like Spearman did, using a statistical technique called factor analysis.

7
00:00:32,570 --> 00:00:36,890
This is an advanced statistical technique, so I’m just going to very briefly outline

8
